We will start by adding opening and closing table tags to define our HVM table.

5
00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:28.060
Next we will add in an opening and closing table row tag to add a row to our table.

6
00:00:28.340 --> 00:00:33.440
Since this is the first row in our table we will use the table heading tag to add table headings for

7
00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:37.380
the columns in our table.

8
00:00:37.430 --> 00:00:39.800
We can then add another row to our table.

9
00:00:39.860 --> 00:00:45.980
We will use the TDA tag to add cells to our table and we'll name our cells cell one cell 2 and cell

10
00:00:45.990 --> 00:00:47.460
3 respectively.

11
00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:56.160
We will add a third row to our table and add three more cells cell 4 cell 5 and cell 6 to see our table.

12
00:00:56.180 --> 00:00:58.230
Let's go to the web browser and run our code

13
00:01:01.140 --> 00:01:05.310
