14
00:01:05.310 --> 00:01:08.660
Let's jump back to the editor.

15
00:01:08.990 --> 00:01:15.080
Now that we have a table we can use some style properties to stylize it using the border property we

16
00:01:15.080 --> 00:01:21.440
can add a border of a specified style with and color around each cell in our table and around the table

17
00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:22.310
itself.

18
00:01:22.580 --> 00:01:27.330
We will apply this style to the table so that there is a border around our table.

19
00:01:27.350 --> 00:01:33.340
We will also apply this style to our table heading elements so that it is applied to each table heading.

20
00:01:33.350 --> 00:01:38.540
Additionally we will apply this style to our table cells using the tag

21
